Module NNERuntimeBasicCpu
Header /Engine/Plugins/Experimental/NNERuntimeBasicCpu/Source/NNERuntimeBasicCpu/Public/NNERuntimeBasicCpuBuilder.h
Include #include "NNERuntimeBasicCpuBuilder.h"

Syntax

class FModelBuilder

Remarks

This class can be used to construct Models for use with the Basic CPU Runtime. Effectively it works by constructing the model in-memory and then serializing this out to create a FileData object which can then be loaded with NNE.

Note: If you pass your own views into this model builder they must out-live the builder itself as it will not create internal copies.
